Find customers who visited but did not make any transactions: You need to identify visits that do not have any associated transactions.
Counting such visits: After identifying these customers, you need to count how many visits of that customer had no transactions.

 SELECT customer_id, COUNT(customer_id) AS count_no_trans
    FROM Visits
    LEFT JOIN Transactions On Transactions.visit_id = Visits.visit_id
    WHERE transaction_id IS NULL
    GROUP BY customer_id ORDER BY count(customer_id) DESC; 
